org.apache.ugli
Interface ULogger

All Known Implementing Classes:
Category, JDK14Logger, NOPLogger, SimpleLogger
public interface ULogger

The main user inteface to logging. It is expected that logging takes places through concerete implemetations of the ULogger interface.

Author:
